1) First Command in Terminal // 

git add . ( THEN PRESS ENTER) = THIS ADDS ALL YOUR CHANGES

2) Second Command in Terminal // 

git commit -m " Update Label " ( THEN PRESS ENTER ) = THIS LABELS THE UPDATE THAT YOU ARE PUSHING 

3) Third Command in Terminal // 

git push ( THEN PRESS ENTER ) = THIS PUSHES YOUR UPDATEd CODE TO YOUR REPOSITORY ( CODE DATABASE )
